Kuku Kube is available for free on Facebook, Android, iOS and on desktop browsers . 
  On each board, one of the squares is a slightly different shade of the same colour . 
  Aim is to find the odd square by tapping it with your finger or clicking with the mouse . 
  Scores lower than 11 are poor and a score higher than 31 means your eyesight is 'great' The game starts with a board of four and grows to 81 squares . 
  Players get a point for every correct square identified . 
 